Configuration
API integrations can be configured in the system settings panel.
{
  "api_settings": {
    "enabled": true,
    "auth_method": "oauth2",
    "rate_limit": 100,
    "webhook_url": "https://your-system.example.com/webhooks/dummyinc",
    "secrets": {
      "client_id": "YOUR_CLIENT_ID",
      "client_secret": "YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET"
    }
  }
}
